msgid "generation"
msgstr ""

#: of prepshot._model.generation:1
msgid ""
"This module contains constraints related to technology generation. The "
"power output of storage and each dispatchable (exclude hydropower) "
"technology (:math:`{\\rm{power}}_{h,m,y,z,e}`) is limited by the existing"
" installed capacity (:math:`{\\rm{cap}}_{y,z,e}^{\\rm{existingtech}}`) "
"and minimum technical output, as follows:"
msgstr ""

#: of prepshot._model.generation:7
msgid ""
"{\\underline{{\\rm{POWER}}}}_{h,m,y,z,e}\\times\n"
"{\\rm{cap}}_{y,z,e}^{\\rm{existingtech}}\\le{\\rm{power}}_{h,m,y,z,e}\\le"
"\n"
"{\\rm{cap}}_{y,z,e}^{\\rm{existingtech}}\\quad\\forall h,m,y,z,e\\in\n"
"{\\mathcal{STOR}}\\ \\&\\ {\\mathcal{DISP}}"
msgstr ""

#: of prepshot._model.generation:14
msgid ""
"Since hydropower processes are explicitly modelled at the plant level in "
"PREP-SHOT, total hydropower output in zone :math:`z` "
"(:math:`{\\rm{power}}_{h,m,y,z,e={\\rm{hydro}}}`) is the sum of the "
"plant-level hydropower output "
"(:math:`{\\rm{power}}_{\\it{s,h,m,y}}^{\\rm{hydro}}`):"
msgstr ""

#: of prepshot._model.generation:20
msgid ""
"{\\rm{power}}_{h,m,y,z,e={\\rm{hydro}}}=\\sum_{s\\in{\\mathcal{SZ}}_z}\n"
"{\\rm{power}}_{s,h,m,y}^{\\rm{hydro}}\\quad\\forall h,m,y,z"
msgstr ""

#: of prepshot._model.generation:25
msgid ""
"Here, calculation of :math:`{\\rm{power}}^{\\rm{hydro}}_{s,h,m,y}` is "
"obtained by external net water head simulation procedure. In addition, "
":math:`{\\rm{power}}^{\\rm{hydro}}_{s,h,m,y}` is bounded between the "
"guaranteed minimum output "
"(:math:`{\\underline{{\\rm{POWER}}}}_s^{\\rm{hydro}}`) and the nameplate "
"capacity (:math:`{{\\rm{CAP}}}_s^{\\rm{hydro}}`), as follows:"
msgstr ""

#: of prepshot._model.generation:31
msgid ""
"Regardless of the technology type, actual power generation "
"(:math:`{\\rm{gen}}_{h,m,y,z,e}`) in a corresponding period "
":math:`\\Delta h` can be calculated based on the power output "
"(:math:`{\\rm{power}}_{h,m,y,z,e}`) and the generation efficiency "
"(:math:`\\eta_{y,e}^{\\rm{out}}`):"
msgstr ""

#: of prepshot._model.generation:36
msgid ""
"{\\rm{gen}}_{h,m,y,z,e} = {\\rm{power}}_{h,m,y,z,e}\\times\\Delta h\n"
"\\times\\eta_{y,e}^{\\rm{out}}\\quad \\forall h,m,y,z,e\\in {\\mathcal{E}}"
msgstr ""

#: of prepshot._model.generation:41
msgid ""
"Note that :math:`\\eta_{y,e}^{\\rm{out}}=1` when :math:`e\\in "
"{\\mathcal{E}}\\backslash {\\mathcal{STOR}}`."
msgstr ""

#: of prepshot._model.generation:44
msgid ""
"All technologies apart from dispatchable technology are limited by the "
"so-called ramping capability, meaning that the variation of their power "
"output in two successive periods is limited.  We introduce two non-"
"negative auxiliary variables: increment (:math:`{ m{power}}_{h,m,y,z,e}^{"
" m{up}}`) and decrement (:math:`{ m{power}}_{h,m,y,z,e}^{ m{down}}`) to "
"describe changes in power output in two successive periods (from "
":math:`h`-1 to :math:`h`) as follows:"
msgstr ""

#: of prepshot._model.generation:55
msgid ""
"{\\rm{power}}_{h,m,y,z,e}^{\\rm{up}}-{\\rm{power}}_{h,m,y,z,e}^{\\rm{down}}"
"\n"
"={\\rm{power}}_{h,m,y,z,e}-{\\rm{power}}_{h-1,m,y,z,e}\n"
"\\quad\\forall h,m,y,z,e\\ \\in {\\mathcal{E}}\\backslash "
"{\\mathcal{NDISP}}"
msgstr ""

#: of prepshot._model.generation:61
msgid ""
"When the power plant ramps up from :math:`h`-1 to :math:`h`, the minimum "
"of :math:`{\\rm{power}}_{h,m,y,z,e}^{\\rm{up}}` is obtained when "
":math:`{\\rm{power}}_{h,m,y,z,e}^{\\rm{down}}` becomes zero. Similarly, "
"when the power plant ramps down from :math:`h`-1 to :math:`h`, the "
"minimum of :math:`{\\rm{power}}_{h,m,y,z,e}^{\\rm{down}}` is obtained "
"when :math:`{\\rm{power}}_{h,m,y,z,e}^{\\rm{up}}` becomes zero. "
"Therefore, we can constrain the maximum ramping up and down respectively,"
" as follows:"
msgstr ""

#: of prepshot._model.generation:69
msgid ""
"{\\rm{power}}_{h,m,y,z,e}^{\\rm{up}}\\le{{R}}_e^{\\rm{up}}\\times\n"
"\\Delta h\\times {\\rm{cap}}_{y,z,e}^{\\rm{existingtech}}\\quad\n"
"\\forall h,m,y,z,e\\in {\\mathcal{E}}\\backslash {\\mathcal{NDISP}}"
msgstr ""

#: of prepshot._model.generation:75
msgid ""
"{\\rm{power}}_{h,m,y,z,e}^{\\rm{down}}\\le{{R}}_e^{\\rm{down}}\\times\n"
"\\Delta h\\times {\\rm{cap}}_{y,z,e}^{\\rm{existingtech}}\n"
"\\quad\\forall h,m,y,z,e\\in {\\mathcal{E}}\\backslash {\\mathcal{NDISP}}"
msgstr ""

#: of prepshot._model.generation:81
msgid ""
"where :math:`{{R}}_e^{\\rm{up}}$/${{R}}_e^{\\rm{down}}` is the allowed "
"maximum/minimum ramping up/down capacity of technology :math:`e` in two "
"successive periods, expressed as a percentage of the existing capacity of"
" storage technology :math:`e`."
msgstr ""

